<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-eyebrow">Policy Consultant</view>
    <view class="hero-title">把复杂政策，翻译成客户能马上听懂的话。</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">
      面向人才认定、补贴、住房、创业扶持等场景，当前页面会按账号权限自动决定走 AI 答复还是知识库兜底。
    </view>
    <view class="meta-row">
      <view class="meta-pill">{{skill ? skill.skillName : '技能准备中'}}</view>
      <view class="meta-pill">{{canUseAi ? 'AI 优先' : '知识库兜底'}}</view>
      <view class="meta-pill">{{sessionInfo && sessionInfo.id ? ('会话 #' + sessionInfo.id) : '会话未建立'}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel-card">
    <view class="section-title">快捷提问</view>
    <view class="section-note">先用高频问题把链路跑通，再慢慢扩展更复杂的政策场景。</view>
    <view class="tile-grid">
      <button
        wx:for="{{quickPrompts}}"
        wx:key="*this"
        class="quick-button"
        data-prompt="{{item}}"
        bindtap="handleQuickPrompt"
        disabled="{{loading || asking || !canUseAgent}}"
      >
        {{item}}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel-card">
    <view class="card-title-row">
      <view>
        <view class="section-title">咨询对话</view>
        <view class="section-note">{{helperText}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="ghost-button" bindtap="handleNewSession" disabled="{{loading || asking || !skill}}">
        新会话
      </button>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="empty-state">政策咨询能力加载中...</view>
    <view wx:elif="{{errorMessage}}" class="empty-state">{{errorMessage}}</view>
    <scroll-view
      wx:else
      class="message-list"
      scroll-y="true"
      style="max-height: 760rpx;"
      scroll-into-view="{{scrollIntoView}}"
    >
      <view wx:if="{{!messages.length}}" class="empty-state">
        可以直接问政策问题。
        建议一次只问一个主问题，比如“厦门市高层次人才住房补贴怎么判断适用条件？”
      </view>
      <view
        wx:for="{{messages}}"
        wx:key="anchorId"
        id="{{item.anchorId}}"
        class="{{item.bubbleClass}}"
      >
        <view class="message-role">{{item.roleText}}</view>
        <view class="message-text">{{item.messageText}}</view>
        <view wx:if="{{item.citations.length}}" class="message-citations">
          依据：{{item.citations.join(' / ')}}
        </view>
      </view>
      <view wx:if="{{asking}}" class="message-bubble message-bubble--assistant">
        <view class="message-role">政策顾问</view>
        <view class="message-text">正在整理政策依据，请稍候...</view>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class="composer-card">
    <view class="field-label">你的问题</view>
    <textarea
      class="textarea-input"
      value="{{question}}"
      maxlength="500"
      placeholder="例如：厦门市新引进人才有哪些补贴，申请时要注意什么？"
      bindinput="handleQuestionInput"
      disabled="{{loading || asking || !canUseAgent}}"
    />
    <view class="button-row" style="margin-top: 18rpx;">
      <button class="primary-button" bindtap="handleSend" disabled="{{loading || asking || !canUseAgent}}">
        {{asking ? '发送中...' : '发送咨询'}}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
